# zlib CVE in Alpine base image — fixed in zlib 1.3.2-r0 but node:20-alpine
# ships with 1.3.1-r2. Will be resolved when Alpine updates the base image.
# Not exploitable in this application context (no user-controlled zlib input).
CVE-2026-22184

# These CVEs are in devDependencies referenced in vendor package.json metadata
# files (e.g., winston/package.json lists eslint as a devDependency).
# The vulnerable packages are NOT installed in the production image.
# Trivy flags them because it reads package.json metadata, not actual installs.

# cross-spawn (devDependency of winston via cross-spawn-async)
CVE-2024-21538

# glob (devDependency of various packages)
CVE-2025-64756

# minimatch (devDependency of eslint referenced in winston metadata)
CVE-2026-26996
CVE-2026-27903
CVE-2026-27904

# tar (devDependency metadata only)
CVE-2026-23745
CVE-2026-23950
CVE-2026-24842
CVE-2026-26960
CVE-2026-29786
CVE-2026-31802
